01:29:42,043 --> 01:29:43,374
Mi-yeon!

910
01:29:45,012 --> 01:29:49,881
Sbohem, má lásko.

911
01:29:50,518 --> 01:29:52,076
Mi-yeon.

912
01:29:54,222 --> 01:29:57,988
Neopouštěj mě.
Prosím, Mi-yeon!

913
01:29:59,327 --> 01:30:00,692
Mi-yeon.

914
01:30:02,130 --> 01:30:03,688
<i>Buď, prosím, šťastný!</i>

915
