Neopouštěj mě!

916
01:30:06,934 --> 01:30:08,196
Mi-yeon.

917
01:30:08,336 --> 01:30:10,600
Navždycky budu s tebou.

918
01:30:11,239 --> 01:30:13,901
Mi-yeon.

919
01:30:15,643 --> 01:30:17,474
Miluju tě!

920
